    "body": "Here's a similar one that will fail for different reasons: (EDIT by bblum: same as edit above)\n\n```\n// Trying to generate races between killing tasks, sending, and deleting ports\nfn main() {\n    for iter::repeat(100u) {\n        let builder = task::builder();\n        task::unsupervise(builder);\n        do task::run(builder) {\n            let po = comm::port();\n            let ch = comm::chan(po);\n            let builder = task::builder();\n            task::unsupervise(builder);\n            do task::run(builder) {\n                comm::send(ch, ());\n            }\n            do task::spawn {\n                fail;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n",
